# Documentation Discipline

If you change:

- Domain entities or fields
- API routes
- Database schema
- Visibility rules
- Auth behavior
- Storage layout (S3 keys)
- Major architectural decisions

Then update:

- docs/PRODUCT.md
- docs/ARCHITECTURE.md
- docs/DECISIONS.md (for non-trivial decisions)

Documentation is part of the definition of done.
